OL,3,CMan accused of stirring up hatred has
OL,4,Ccase moved after wrong charge put to
OL,5,Chim
OL,7,FA man accused of publishing
OL,8,Fthreatening material intended to stir
OL,9,Fup religious hatred on social media
OL,10,Fhas had his sentencing hearing
OL,11,Fpostponed after the wrong charge was
OL,12,Fput to him.
OL,14,FGeraint Boyce, 43, of Penrhiw-Fer,
OL,15,FTonypandy, was due to be sentenced
OL,16,Fwhen he appeared before Merthyr Tydfil
OL,17,FCrown Court on Friday, 16 August.
