OL,7,FBut the court heard that the charge
OL,8,Fput to Boyce was incorrect when he
OL,9,Fappeared before Cardiff Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt earlier this week.
OL,12,FThe charge relates to a post on
OL,13,FFacebook on or around July 31 in
OL,14,Frelation to recent UK public disorder.
