OL,7,FThe Recorder Of Cardiff, Judge Tracey
OL,8,FLloyd-Clarke adjourned the sentencing
OL,9,Funtil September 10.
OL,11,FAddressing Boyce she said: "As you
OL,12,Fhave heard, there is some confusion
OL,13,Fover the charge you have pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to."
OL,16,FShe said the delay would allow time
OL,17,Ffor a pre-sentence report to be
OL,18,Fcreated and Mr Taylor to read through
OL,19,Fmitigation documents.
